&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;author-description&#34;&gt;How to use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using Atlas requires a browser with Javascript enabled.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can find the typological features through the item «Categories» in the sidebar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All maps are provided with the fullscreen view via button «&lt;span class=&#34;scaps&#34;&gt;FULLSCREEN&lt;/span&gt;» under each map.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

